embeddedItem.name: Immersifier
embeddedItem.desc: This item can be exchanged by spending <nobr>40</nobr> Trailblaze Power, and is used to exchange for Immersion Rewards in the Simulated Universe
embeddedItem.lore:
This digitized Trailblaze Power can only be used in the Simulated Universe.

"Explore, understand, establish, and connect — that is what it means to trailblaze. Akivili may have fallen, but their legacy continues!"
